title: Ebro In The Morning - Isaiah Rashad + Parenting With Ebro

itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 8/5. Isaiah Rashad talks about his new album "The House Is Burning," now streaming! 

Ebro and the crew discuss LOX vs. Dipset, Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments, and you find out who played themselves.
